search_trade_card_close_20260324.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_control_tower_20260324.md`\n- `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/live_scheduler_v1.json`\n- `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/logs/paper_profiles_cron.log`\n- `scripts/investment_research_paper_bridge.py`\n\n一句话结论：\n\n**根因不是“刷新超时”，而是“15:20 收盘播报早于 16:30 模拟盘刷新，而桥接脚本还错误地按 15:05 作为当日应刷新时点”，导致收盘视图误报过期。**\n\n我已经把这次追因落到执行清单并提交了记录：\n- 提交：`22faee1`\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接给出**修复方案清单**，明确改哪两个点最稳：\n- 方案 A：收盘 bundle 延后到 paper profiles 之后\n- 方案 B：bridge 不再写死 15:05，改为读取 `live_scheduler_v1.json`\n- 方案 C：15:20 前只显示“待收盘刷新”，不判 stale","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fb068e88b60a2b20169c25cca719881949f13bb679e869658\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":73488,"output":1113,"cacheRead":38400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113001,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774345403371}}
